2. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper discusses the performance of full-duplex relaying systems, which is a topic related to networking and internet architecture.
3. cs.SI (Systems and Control) - The paper deals with the analysis and optimization of full-duplex relaying systems, which is a topic related to systems and control.
4. cs.COMM (Computer Communications and Networks) - The paper discusses the performance of communication systems in the presence of self-interference, which is a topic related to computer communications and networks.
